LanguageData.ATR_Tier3Android.label: T3 Android
LanguageData.ATR_Tier3Android.description: Androids classified as tier three are often qualified by their large stature - standing at a height ranging from seven to nine feet - and impressive capabilities. They are incredibly durable, modular, and capable. Requiring extensive amounts of rare resources, they are generally only mass-produced on glitterworlds.
